cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.LO, cs.SY. 

The paper deals with the problem of synthesizing a controller for a robot with a surveillance objective, which involves game theory (cs.GT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and logic (cs.LO). The use of abstraction to mitigate the exponential blow-up typically incurred by such transformations suggests the paper may also belong to the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
